snippet.title: 15 of nature's most spectacular shows
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Some signs of normalcy after Indonesian volcano eruption
snippet.description:
* Some things returned to normal in Indonesia on Saturday after a volcano erupted two days before, but tens of thousands of evacuees were yet to return to their homes.
http://www.cnn.com/2014/02/15/world/asia/indonesia-volcano-eruption-evacuation/index.html

snippet.title: Indonesian volcano erupts, killing 3 and grounding flights
snippet.description:
* A volcano eruption in Indonesia killed three people and forced tens of thousands more out of their homes, the disaster management agency said Friday.
http://www.cnn.com/2014/02/13/world/asia/indonesia-volcano-eruption-evacuation/index.html

snippet.title: Indonesia volcano: Mount Sinabung eruption intensifies
snippet.description:
* A volcanic eruption in Indonesia that has displaced more than 22,000 people is intensifying, local authorities say.
http://www.cnn.com/2014/01/09/world/asia/indonesia-volcano-erupts/index.html

snippet.title: El Salvador's Chaparrastique volcano erupts for first time in 37 years
snippet.description:
* El Salvador's Chaparrastique volcano erupted Sunday, sending a dark cloud of ash miles into the sky, forcing thousands to evacuate from their homes and snarling travel in the Central American country as airlines canceled flights.
http://www.cnn.com/2013/12/29/world/americas/el-salvador-chaparrastique-volcano-erupts/index.html

snippet.title: Erupting volcano spawns island off Japan
snippet.description:
* Japan is getting bigger and bigger and bigger -- one volcanic blast at a time.
http://www.cnn.com/2013/11/22/world/asia/japan-volcano-forms-island/index.html

snippet.title: Thousands evacuated after volcano eruption in Indonesia
snippet.description:
* A volcano in Indonesia prompted the evacuation of more than 6,000 people this weekend, blanketing buildings and cars in ashes, emergency officials said Monday.
